Gold One Signs Funding Agreements With Investec for Rand Uranium Purchase

-- B y   V i c t o r i a   B a t c h e l o r
-- 
2011-08-28T22:41:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-28/gold-one-signs-funding-agreements-with-investec-for-rand-uranium-purchase.html
Gold One International Ltd. (GDO)  has
signed financing agreements with Investec Bank Ltd. to give
effect to the acquisition of Rand Uranium, according to a
regulatory filing. The agreements provide for a total facility
of 1.47 billion rand, the company said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Victoria Batchelor at 
 vbatchelor@bloomberg.net  